   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To reset the password all the NMC must be reset to its default
settings. This will remove all the configurations on the NMC, including
the passwords.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To reset the NMC:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Hold down the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reset button</uicontrol> for 20-25
seconds, as long as the status LED is green.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">As soon as the status LED changes to orange release the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reset button</uicontrol>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Let the NMC reboot and start up again.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">The IP address, network settings, user settings and any other
settings will need to be configured again.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </p>
